content: I'm in the market for a new laptop, and I was wondering if you could help me compare some models from HP and Dell. I recently checked out some options at Best Buy, but I didn't have a chance to really dive into the specs. Oh, and by the way, I've been using my new portable power bank from Mophie a lot lately - I got it on Amazon for $39.99 on February 20th, which was a great deal considering it was originally $69.99.
